      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how heavy and overwhelming that feeling of hopelessness can be. It makes sense that when the news constantly highlights global crises, it can make even simple goals like building a future feel pointless. Many people feel this same way, but it's worth noting that while the planet faces serious challenges, there are also countless individuals and communities actively working to address these issues. Sometimes, shifting focus to local actions or small, positive steps can help regain a sense of agency and purpose.",
      "source": "target",
